cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.MA

The paper discusses the design and specification of algorithms and software to monitor and govern complex physical situations with multiple modes of behavior. This suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), software engineering (cs.SE), and machine learning (cs.MA). The examples given in the paper, such as driverless racing cars, also support these sub-categories.
